[[File:Fuerth Stadttheater 3.jpg|thumb|Stadttheater Fürth]]
'''Stadttheater Fürth''' is a theatre in [[Bavaria]], [[Germany]]. It was designed by the Viennese architecture office [[Fellner & Helmer]], and completed in 1902.<ref name="AZW">[http://www.architektenlexikon.at/de/126.htm Architekturzentrum Wien: "Ferdinand Fellner II."], (''in German''), retrieved 30 March 2013</ref>

