'''Yugoslavia''' participated in the '''Eurovision Song Contest 1976''' in [[The Hague]].   [[Ambasadori]] represented Yugoslavia with the song "[[Ne mogu skriti svoju bol]]". Ambasadori scored 10 points (highest 4 from France) placing 17th.<ref>Eurovision Song Contest 1976</ref>

